nodes.text: Air Strike is a single-player online flash player game found on StarWars.com. It was posted on StarWars.com as a supplement to The Clone Wars television series. Game play is set during the First Battle of Felucia.
Clone forces are under siege on jungles of Felucia! General Plo Koon is dispatching his aerial forces to support the ground troops already pinned down in the jungles.
Your mission is to blast through enemy forces and take out the Separatist command ship. Be cautious though, because the droids are deeply entrenched and well supplied!
